                    <name>
                        <ln>Stuart</ln>
                        <pf>Mr.</pf>
                    </name>
                </names>
                <summary>Anderson requested the Vindicator correct the SS for claiming that he is a
                    Whig. SS made a mistake when they reported that Anderson siad he was no
